ğŸ“‹ TECHNICAL APPENDIX

Quick Reference - Security Headers:

# Recommended Security Headers  
Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'  
Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains  
X-Frame-Options: DENY  
X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff  
Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin

Quick Reference - Cookie Security:

# Secure Cookie Attributes  
Set-Cookie: session_id=value; HttpOnly; Secure; SameSite=Strict; Path=/  
Set-Cookie: token=value; HttpOnly; Secure; SameSite=Lax; Max-Age=86400

Quick Reference - CORS Security:

# Secure CORS Configuration  
Access-Control-Allow-Origin: https://trusted-domain.com  
Access-Control-Allow-Methods: GET, POST, OPTIONS  
Access-Control-Allow-Headers: Content-Type, Authorization  
Access-Control-Max-Age: 86400


